HEADWORD: Censurable
<hw>Cen"sur*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Deserving of
censure; blamable; culpable; reprehensible; <as>as, a
<ex>censurable</ex> person, or <ex>censurable</ex>
conduct</as>.</def></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Cen"sur*a*bleness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Cen"sur*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Censure</ent>⟦br⟧
